I'm craving another goat cheese, rosemary, fig, and date crepe. It was rich and delicious! Paired with a french press coffee and I couldn't have been happier. Adorable quaint environment with an explosion of Parisian paraphernalia on the walls. Perfect place to meet a friend, bring your mom when she's in town, or sit and get some work done. And of course the dessert crepe with baked apples and whipped cream and ice cream was decadent. A nice little corner french cafe...
